<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Partnership Inquiry Received - MEDH</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f8fafc;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #48bb78 0%, #38a169 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .header-subtitle {
        font-size: 16px;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .inquiry-details {
        background-color: #f0fff4;
        border: 1px solid #9ae6b4;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      .detail-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #c6f6d5;
      }

      .detail-row:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .detail-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #276749;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .detail-value {
        color: #2d3748;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .inquiry-id {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #48bb78 0%, #38a169 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 3px 10px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .process-timeline {
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .timeline-title {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .timeline-steps {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .timeline-step {
        padding: 12px 0;
        border-left: 3px solid #c6f6d5;
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-left: 10px;
        position: relative;
      }

      .timeline-step:before {
        content: "";
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: #48bb78;
        position: absolute;
        left: -7px;
        top: 16px;
      }

      .step-title {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .step-description {
        color: #4a5568;
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-top: 4px;
      }

      .contact-info {
        background-color: #edf7ed;
        border-left: 4px solid #48bb78;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        margin: 25px 0;
      }

      .contact-title {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2d3748;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #2d3748;
        color: #a0aec0;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .footer-logo {
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .footer-links {
        margin: 15px 0;
      }

      .footer-links a {
        color: #48bb78;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 10px;
      }

      .footer-links a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .disclaimer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #718096;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-container {
          margin: 0;
          border-radius: 0;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 25px 20px;
        }

        .detail-row {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 5px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">ü§ù MEDH</div>
        <div class="header-subtitle">Educational Partnerships</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">
          Dear
          {{representative_name}},
        </div>

        <p>Thank you for submitting your application to partner with Medh! We
          are delighted that
          <strong>{{school_name}}</strong>
          is interested in collaborating with us to bring innovative skill
          development programs to your students.</p>

        <!-- Inquiry Details -->
        <div class="inquiry-details">
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Inquiry ID:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">
              <span class="inquiry-id">{{inquiry_id}}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Institution:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{school_name}}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Institution Type:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{institution_type}}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Submission Date:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">{{formatDate
                submitted_at
                "MMMM DD, YYYY"
              }}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-row">
            <div class="detail-label">Status:</div>
            <div class="detail-value">Under Review</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Your Inquiry ID: {{inquiry_id}}</strong></p>

        <p>We have successfully received your partnership inquiry submitted
          through our website. Our educational partnerships team is reviewing
          your information with great interest, as we are always excited to
          connect with forward-thinking institutions committed to enhancing
          student learning experiences.</p>

        <!-- Process Timeline -->
        <div class="process-timeline">
          <div class="timeline-title">üöÄ Here's what you can expect over the
            coming weeks:</div>
          <ul class="timeline-steps">
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Initial Review (2-3 business days)</div>
              <div class="step-description">Our partnerships team will evaluate
                your application and institutional profile</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Preliminary Discussion (Week 1)</div>
              <div class="step-description">A partnership coordinator will
                contact you to schedule an initial conversation about mutual
                goals and expectations</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Needs Assessment (Week 2)</div>
              <div class="step-description">We'll work together to identify
                specific skill development programs that align with your
                curriculum and student needs</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Partnership Proposal (Week 3)</div>
              <div class="step-description">Our team will develop a customized
                partnership plan including program offerings, implementation
                timeline, and resource requirements</div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-step">
              <div class="step-title">Agreement Finalization (Week 4-5)</div>
              <div class="step-description">Review and finalization of
                partnership terms and operational details</div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>We aim to reach out within
          <strong>2 business days</strong>
          to schedule the preliminary discussion. This conversation will help us
          better understand your institution's specific needs and how Medh's
          programs can complement your educational objectives.</p>

        <p>Our partnerships are built on shared values of educational
          innovation, practical skill development, and preparing students for
          future success. We're excited about the possibility of collaborating
          with your institution to achieve these goals.</p>

        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-title">ü§ù Educational Partnerships Division</div>
          <p>If you have any immediate questions or would like to provide
            additional information about your institution, please contact our
            Partnerships Team:</p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> partnerships@medh.co</p>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +91 77108 40696</p>
          <p><strong>Please reference your Inquiry ID:
              {{inquiry_id}}
              in all communications.</strong></p>
        </div>

        <p>We look forward to exploring this partnership opportunity with you
          and thank you for considering Medh as your skill development education
          partner.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
          <strong>Warm regards,</strong><br />
          Partnerships Team<br />
          <strong>MEDH Learning Platform</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-logo">MEDH</div>
        <div>Transforming education through innovative partnerships</div>

        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="https://www.medh.co/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
          |
          <a href="https://www.medh.co/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a>
          |
          <a href="mailto:partnerships@medh.co">Contact Partnerships</a>
        </div>

        <div class="disclaimer">
          <p>&copy;
            {{currentYear}}
            MEDH Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 10px;">This email confirms receipt of your
            partnership inquiry. Our team will be in touch within 2 business
            days to discuss next steps.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
            <strong>MEDH Learning Platform</strong><br />
            üìß partnerships@medh.co | üìû +91 77108 40696<br />
            üåê
            <a
              href="https://www.medh.co"
              style="color: #48bb78;"
            >www.medh.co</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>